author: Victoria Hernandez
title: Freddie Gibbs Announces His Return

organizations.name: freddie gibbs announces his return freddie gibbs

text:
Freddie Gibbs Announces His Return March 6, 2017 | 1:51 PM 6 
Freddie Gibbs seems ready to return to the public eye after being acquitted of rape charges in Austria in September. 
Since he was found not guilty , the Piñata rapper was fairly quiet on all fronts, but posted a montage of a painting with opera music on Instagram today (March 6) with a simple caption. A post shared by Kane (@freddiegibbs) on Mar 6, 2017 at 9:44am PST 
“The Return” is also the name of a track from Danny Brown’s Old album that featured Gibbs. 
This is Gibbs’ first Instagram post in 22 weeks as his last upload to the social media site was him celebrating his freedom with his daughter. A post shared by Kane (@freddiegibbs) on Oct 1, 2016 at 1:13am PDT 
In January, Gibbs shared “ Overtime ” from the vault to keep his fans engaged and a month later, appeared on iLL Brown’s “ Friends ” single. 
He also popped up on the slopes via Currensy’s IG feed. A post shared by spitta_andretti (@spitta_andretti) on Jan 4, 2017 at 12:07pm PST 
Gibbs’ last full-length musical output was 2015’s Shadow of a Doubt , which received a 4.0 rating from HipHopDX.
